    "name": "Myrmidon Robot",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Myrmidons are highly mobile robots programmed to patrol the skies above important locations. They react with swift violence, interpret anomalous sensory input as proof of hostile intent and rain destruction on the offending target immediately and without mercy. Most have been programmed to communicate, but they rarely hesitate in their carnage to do so."
        }
    ],
